
    GnollHack version 4.0.3

Options compiled into this edition:

    color, data librarian, end-of-game dumplogs, exclusive lock on level 0
    file, insurance files for recovering from crashes, log file, extended
    log file, errors and warnings log file, news file, pattern matching via
    :PATMATCH:, pseudo random numbers generated by ISAAC64, strong PRNG seed
    available from CNG BCryptGenRandom(), restore saved games via menu,
    screen clipping, screen control via WIN32 console I/O, traditional
    status display, status via windowport with highlighting, user sounds,
    system configuration at run-time, save and bones files accepted from
    versions 3.6.0 through 4.0.3, and basic GnollHack features.

Supported windowing systems:

    "tty" (traditional text with optional line-drawing) and "mswin", with a
    default of "mswin".

